qh realms                                   show all Questhub realms

qh reaml --id <rid>                         show information about realm
qh reaml quests --id <rid>                  show open quests for the specified realm

qh quests --player <player>                 show open quests for the specified player
qh quests --self                            show open quests for authenticated player

qh quest --id <qid>                         show information about the quest
qh quest new  --id <rid> --title <title>    create new quest
qh quest claim --id <qid>                   claim points for the quest
qh quest leave --id <qid>                   leave the quest
qh quest abandon --id <qid>                 abandon the quest
